snippet.title: Missing Parts - The Tantei Stories Complete (見習偵探物語 完全版) PSP
snippet.description:
Running on ppsspp
Missing Parts - The Tantei Stories Complete
見習偵探物語 完全版

this story was originally launched for Dreamcast in 3 volumes
and later for PS2 as two parts (side A and B) including a new scenario

and now for the PSP they brought back the content from ps2 
+ yet another new chapter

#psp #fog #nipponichi
#visualnovel #revivalhorror
